prompt:
Add a public class called Counter to Domain.calr with a private field called _count of type i32.

Use this exact Calor field syntax:
§CL{c001:Counter:pub}
  §FLD{i32:_count:priv}
§/CL{c001}

The §FLD{type:name:visibility} syntax defines a field:
- type is the field type
- name is the field name (private fields often start with _)
- visibility is pub/priv/prot
- Fields are direct storage, unlike properties
